body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for reaching out to us. My name is William Baker and I'm a customer service agent at AutoPro Solutions. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Teresa. To assist you further, could you please provide the last four digits of your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, my phone number ends in two two zero zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Teresa. Additionally, for security purposes, could you confirm the first three digits of your home address postal code?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, the first three digits of my postal code are V eight seven.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for verifying. Is there anything specific you would like to discuss today, Teresa?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm a bit disappointed about a privacy issue related to a recent car purchase.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concern, Teresa. We value your privacy and will address this issue promptly. Thank you for bringing it to our attention.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for sharing this information with us, Teresa. We appreciate your time and patience. If you have any further questions or concerns, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Thank you, have a good day as well.
